<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>CMake on 清松小站</title><link>https://coderqs.github.io/tags/cmake/</link><description>Recent content in CMake on 清松小站</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://coderqs.github.io/tags/cmake/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CMake 介绍与安装</title><link>https://coderqs.github.io/2019/03/cmake-%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://coderqs.github.io/2019/03/cmake-%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="cmake-介绍与安装">CMake 介绍与安装&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="cmake-介绍">CMake 介绍&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://cmake.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>CMake&lt;/a>是一个跨平台的开源的元构建系统，可以构建，测试和打包软件。它可以用于支持多个本机构建环境，包括
make，Apple 的 xcode 和 Microsoft Visual Studio。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="cmake-的安装">CMake 的安装&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="windows">Windows&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>在官网&lt;a class="link" href="https://cmake.org/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>下载&lt;/a>安装包安装即可。&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="centos">Centos&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="安装">安装&lt;/h4>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>yum install -y cmake
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>安装完成后执行下面命令，检查是否成功。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cmake -version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="升级">升级&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>有时候命令安装的版本不够，需要更高的版本，这时就需要手动进行升级。&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>卸载旧的 cmake
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>yum remove -y cmake
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>在官网的下载页面找到需要的 cmake 版本，下载后并解压。我的命令如下:
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>wget https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/releases/download/v3.20.0-rc2/cmake-3.20.0-rc2-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>tar -zxvf cmake-3.20.0-rc2-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>将其复制到你要安装的目录。我安装的目录是 &lt;code>/usr/local/&lt;/code>:
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cp cmake-3.20.0-rc2-linux-x86_64/* /usr/local/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>在 &amp;lsquo;&amp;rsquo;/etc/profile &amp;rsquo;&amp;rsquo; 的最后一行添加你安装的目录，语法为
&lt;code>export PATH=$PATH:你安装的目录/bin&lt;/code>。&lt;strong>我安装的 &lt;code>/usr/local/&lt;/code>
目录是系统默认包含的，所以可以省略这步&lt;/strong>。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>检查是否安装成功。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="可能遇见的问题">可能遇见的问题&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="cmake-error-error-executing-cmakeloadcache-aborting">CMake Error: Error executing cmake::LoadCache(). Aborting&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>这个是我在手动安装 CMake 的时候没有把 &lt;code>share/cmake.***&lt;/code> 的文件也拷过去导致的，拷贝过去就可以了。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>使用 cmake 生成 XCode 工程</title><link>https://coderqs.github.io/2019/03/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-cmake-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-xcode-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://coderqs.github.io/2019/03/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-cmake-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-xcode-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="使用-cmake-生成-xcode-工程">使用 cmake 生成 XCode 工程&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="方法">方法&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>cmake 的构建命令增加参数 `-G &amp;ldquo;Xcode&amp;rdquo;`，例如&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cmake -G Xcode ..
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="遇到的问题">遇到的问题&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="报错找不到编译器">报错找不到编译器&lt;/h4>
&lt;h5 id="错误信息">错误信息&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">11
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>-- The C compiler identification is unknown
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>-- The CXX compiler identification is unknown
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>CMake Error at CMakeLists.txt:2 (project):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> No CMAKE_C_COMPILER could be found.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>CMake Error at CMakeLists.txt:2 (project):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> No CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER could be found.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h5 id="解决方法">解决方法&lt;/h5>
&lt;p>执行命令下面的命令后再重试即可&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
&lt;table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">&lt;tr>&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code>&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#686868">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo xcode-select --switch /Applications/Xcode.app/
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>**注：**执行完命令后要清空 cmake 生成的缓存文件。&lt;/p>
